  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"mc-hero-strip\">\n<div class=\"container mc-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"mc-hero-copy\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb mc-breadcrumb\">\n<a href=\"/resources\">Resources</a>\n<span>/</span>\n<b>Model Community</b>\n</div>\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">MODEL COMMUNITY</span>\n<h1>An open-source 3D model community for makers</h1>\n<p>Browse, collect, comment, and download models of industrial parts shared by other users.\n          Support CNC, 3D printing, sheet metal, injection molding, casting and other manufacturing scenarios.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-hero-actions\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n          Upload Model\n        </a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">Publishing specifications</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mc-community-section\">\n<div class=\"container mc-community-layout\">\n<aside class=\"mc-left-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>Model Channel</h3>\n<nav aria-label=\"Model Channel Filter\" class=\"mc-channel-nav\">\n<button aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"model-category-button active\" data-model-filter=\"all\" type=\"button\">\n<span>recom</span>\n<b>All Models</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"cnc\" type=\"button\">\n<span>CNC</span>\n<b>CNC machining</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"3dprint\" type=\"button\">\n<span>PRINT</span>\n<b>3D Printing</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"sheet\" type=\"button\">\n<span>SHEET</span>\n<b>Sheet metal processing</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"injection\" type=\"button\">\n<span>MOLD</span>\n<b>Injection mold</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"casting\" type=\"button\">\n<span>CAST</span>\n<b>Cast Structures</b>\n</button>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>Common Formats</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-format-cloud\">\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>OBJ</span>\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>SLDPRT</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card mc-upload-mini\">\n<h3>Contribution Model</h3>\n<p>Upload publicly available models to complement materials, workmanship, formatting, and design instructions.</p>\n<a href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">Publish now</a>\n</div>\n</aside>\n<section class=\"mc-feed\">\n<div class=\"mc-feed-top\">\n<form class=\"mc-search-bar\" role=\"search\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M20 20l-4.3-4.3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path>\n</svg>\n<input aria-label=\"Search Objects\" id=\"model-search-input\" placeholder=\"Search for models, materials, processes, formats, e.g. aluminum brackets step\" type=\"search\"/>\n</form>\n<div class=\"mc-sort-box\">\n<select aria-label=\"Model Sorting\" id=\"model-sort-select\">\n<option value=\"hot\">Overall popularity</option>\n<option value=\"downloads\">Best Selling</option>\n<option value=\"likes\">Most liked</option>\n<option value=\"latest\">Last Published</option>\n</select>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-feed-tabs\">\n<button class=\"is-active\" type=\"button\">recom</button>\n<button type=\"button\">Latest</button>\n<button type=\"button\">Follow</button>\n<button type=\"button\">FAQs</button>\n<span id=\"model-result-count\">Total 8 Models</span>\n<button class=\"mc-clear-button\" id=\"model-clear-filter\" type=\"button\">Clear filters</button>\n</div>\n<article class=\"mc-composer-card\">\n<div class=\"mc-composer-avatar\">M</div>\n<div class=\"mc-composer-body\">\n<strong>Share a model or start a manufacturing discussion</strong>\n<p>Can publish model files, structural design issues, process suggestions, DFM questions, or material selection experience.</p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n                Upload Model\n              </a>\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">View Publishing Specifications</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"cnc\" data-comments=\"42\" data-downloads=\"1280\" data-format=\"STEP\" data-hot=\"96\" data-keywords=\"CNC machining of stainless steel shaft type step keyway threads\" data-latest=\"8\" data-likes=\"236\" data-material=\"Stainless steel\" data-model-id=\"precision-shaft\" data-title=\"Step model of precision shaft parts\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">L</div>\n<div>\n<strong>Structural Designer Leo</strong>\n<span>2 hours ago · Published on CNC Machining Channel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Step model for precision shaft parts, suitable for turning quotes and drawing annotation reference</h2>\n<p>The model consists of a multi-step shaft, keyway, thread, chamfer and retracting groove structure.\n              It is suitable for CNC turning process evaluation, shaft part tolerance marking reference, and can also be used as a model inspection sample before quotation.</p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>CNC machining</span>\n<span>Stainless steel</span>\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>Shaft Parts</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>CNC Process Engineer Chen:</strong>The keyway and withdrawal groove are relatively complete. It is recommended to make up a version of the engineering drawing with key shaft diameter tolerances.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"236\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>236</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>Favorites</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"precision-shaft\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>42 Comments</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"precision-shaft\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"Step model of precision shaft parts\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>Share</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"precision-shaft\" type=\"button\">More</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"Model preview (current image occupancy, subsequent access to 3D rendering)\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"Precision shaft part model\" src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>CNC</span>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>precision-shaft.step</b>\n<span>Step · 2.8 MB · Suitable for CNC turning</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/precision-shaft.step\">Download Model</a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\" data-comments=\"35\" data-downloads=\"856\" data-format=\"STL\" data-hot=\"92\" data-keywords=\"3D Printed Metal Printed Titanium Flange STL step Lightweight\" data-latest=\"7\" data-likes=\"198\" data-material=\"Aluminum Alloy\" data-model-id=\"lightweight-flange\" data-title=\"Lightweight flange connector\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">M</div>\n<div>\n<strong>3D printing enthusiast Mina</strong>\n<span>Today · Posted to 3D Printing Channel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Lightweight Flange Connector STL Model for Metal 3D Printed Structural Reference</h2>\n<p>This model retains the flange mounting holes and adds a weight-reducing structure and reinforcing ribs in the middle area.\n              It can be used to refer to the lightweight design of metal 3D printing, and is also suitable for subsequent CNC secondary processing discussions.</p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>3D Printing</span>\n<span>Aluminum Alloy</span>\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>Ascend</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>Material Engineer Yuan:</strong>If titanium alloy is actually used, it is recommended to supplement the lower limit of wall thickness and the post-treatment instructions.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"198\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>198</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>Favorites</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"lightweight-flange\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>35 Comments</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"lightweight-flange\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"Lightweight flange connector\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>Share</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"lightweight-flange\" type=\"button\">\n                More\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"Model preview (current image occupancy, subsequent access to 3D rendering)\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"Lightweight flange connector\" src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>3D PRINT</span>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>lightweight-flange.stl</b>\n<span>STL · 4.1 MB · Suitable for metal printing</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/lightweight-flange.stl\">\n                Download Model\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"sheet\" data-comments=\"76\" data-downloads=\"2110\" data-format=\"DXF\" data-hot=\"98\" data-keywords=\"Sheet Metal Bracket Laser Cutting Bending DXF Aluminum Alloy Expansion\" data-latest=\"6\" data-likes=\"342\" data-material=\"Aluminum alloy\" data-model-id=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" data-title=\"Sheet metal bending bracket\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">A</div>\n<div>\n<strong>Automation Equipment Team AX Lab</strong>\n<span>Yesterday · Posted to Sheet Metal Processing Channel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Sheet metal bending bracket DXF unfolding model, including bending lines and mounting holes</h2>\n<p>Suitable for automated equipment internal bracket reference.Mounting holes, bending lines and reinforcing edges are reserved in the model,\n              It can be used for laser cutting, bending process communication, and is also suitable for DFM inspection examples.</p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>sheet</span>\n<span>Aluminum alloy</span>\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>Bending</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>Sheet metal engineer Zhou:</strong>It is recommended to write the plate thickness and bending radius at the time of release, and the actual processing will be more accurate.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"342\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>342</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>Favorites</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>76 Comments</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"Sheet metal bending bracket\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>Share</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" type=\"button\">\n                More\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"Model preview (current image occupancy, subsequent access to 3D rendering)\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"Sheet metal bending bracket\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>SHEET</span>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>sheet-metal-bracket.dxf</b>\n<span>DXF · 1.3 MB · with expanded structure</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/sheet-metal-bracket.dxf\">\n                Download Model\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"cnc\" data-comments=\"31\" data-downloads=\"756\" data-format=\"IGES\" data-hot=\"81\" data-keywords=\"CNC 5-Axis Aluminum Alloy IGES Cavity Curved Shaped Parts\" data-latest=\"5\" data-likes=\"151\" data-material=\"Aluminum alloy\" data-model-id=\"complex-cavity\" data-title=\"Complex cavity parts\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">F</div>\n<div>\n<strong>5-axis machining notes</strong>\n<span>3 days ago · Posted to CNC Machining Channel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Complex cavity IGES model for five-axis path planning and clamping discussions</h2>\n<p>The model includes special-shaped cavities, curved surface transitions, and multi-angle machining features.\n              It is suitable for discussing five-axis machining accessibility, tool shaft swing, fixture avoidance and CMM inspection schemes.</p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>Five-axis machining</span>\n<span>Aluminum alloy</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>Complex cavity</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>Five Axis Programming Kai:</strong>This model suggests adding a datum description, otherwise there are several different options for the clamping scheme.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"151\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>151</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>Favorites</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"complex-cavity\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>31 Comments</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"complex-cavity\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"Complex cavity parts\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>Share</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"complex-cavity\" type=\"button\">\n                More\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"Model preview (current image occupancy, subsequent access to 3D rendering)\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"Complex cavity parts\" src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>5-AXIS</span>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>complex-cavity.iges</b>\n<span>IGES · 6.5 MB · Curved cavity structure</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/complex-cavity.iges\">\n                Download Model\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"injection\" data-comments=\"21\" data-downloads=\"643\" data-format=\"IGES\" data-hot=\"75\" data-keywords=\"Injection molding ABS housing IGES drawing die parting line snap\" data-latest=\"4\" data-likes=\"126\" data-material=\"ABS\" data-model-id=\"injection-shell\" data-title=\"Injection molding equipment housing\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">T</div>\n<div>\n<strong>Mold Engineer Tang</strong>\n<span>4 days ago · Posted to Injection Mold Channel</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Injection-molded housing IGES model with pull-out slope, snap position and parting line reference</h2>\n<p>Suitable as a reference for the design of injection molding structures.The model includes a housing snap, a thin-walled structure,\n              Drawing slope and parting line area, suitable for discussing injection molding and mold design risks.</p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>Injection molding</span>\n<span>ABS</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>Enclosure Structure</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>Structural designer Qian:</strong>The buckle position is relatively clear, it is recommended to add wall thickness marking and rib position thickness description.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"126\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>126</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>Favorites</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"injection-shell\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>21 Comments</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"injection-shell\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"Injection molding equipment housing\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>Share</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"injection-shell\" type=\"button\">\n                More\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"Model preview (current image occupancy, subsequent access to 3D rendering)\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"Injection molding equipment housing\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>MOLD</span>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>injection-shell.iges</b>\n<span>IGES · 3.2 MB · Injection Molded Enclosure Structure</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/injection-shell.iges\">\n                Download Model\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<div class=\"model-empty-state\" hidden=\"\" id=\"model-empty-state\">\n<strong>No matching models found</strong>\n<span>Try changing the process classification or searching for other materials, formats, part names.</span>\n</div>\n</section>\n<aside class=\"mc-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"mc-side-card mc-profile-card\">\n<div class=\"mc-profile-avatar\">M</div>\n<h3>Welcome to the community of models</h3>\n<p>Log in to publish models, collect content, participate in reviews, and manage your own models.</p>\n<div>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">Upload it</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>Community data</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-stat-list\">\n<div>\n<strong>12,580+</strong>\n<span>Open model</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>8,200+</strong>\n<span>is user active</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>45,000+</strong>\n<span>Monthly downloads</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>Popular Topics</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-topic-list\">\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># step or IGES Which is better for CNC quotes?</strong>\n<span>48 Discussions</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># What are the key dimensions to mark before uploading a thin-walled aluminum model?</strong>\n<span>32 Discussions</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># How do 3D printed models check wall thickness risks in advance?</strong>\n<span>27 Discussions</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># What information needs to be retained for sheet metal unfolding diagrams?</strong>\n<span>19 Discussions</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>Creator Chart</h3>\n<ol class=\"mc-rank-list\">\n<li>\n<span>1</span>\n<div>\n<strong>Structural Designer Leo</strong>\n<b>18 models/326 collections</b>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span>2</span>\n<div>\n<strong>Chen, CNC Process Engineer</strong>\n<b>12 models/289 collections</b>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span>3</span>\n<div>\n<strong>AX Lab Automation Team</strong>\n<b>9 models/241 collections</b>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card mc-rule-card\">\n<h3>Rules of the Blog</h3>\n<p>Do not upload models that involve confidentiality, infringement, or contain sensitive customer information.\n            It is recommended to delete the project number, customer identification, confidential assembly relationship and non-public process details before release.</p>\n</div>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section template-cta\">\n<div class=\"container template-cta-inner\">\n<div>\n<h2>After seeing the appropriate model, do you need to evaluate the actual machining plan?</h2>\n<p>Upload the model and supplement the material, quantity, surface treatment and delivery requirements for process evaluation and quotation.</p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"light-btn\" href=\"/quote?mode=quickQuote#quote-upload\">\n        Quote now\n      </a>\n</div>\n</section>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"model-modal\" hidden=\"\" id=\"model-detail-modal\">\n<div class=\"model-modal-backdrop\" data-model-modal-close=\"\"></div>\n<article aria-labelledby=\"model-modal-title\" aria-modal=\"true\" class=\"model-modal-dialog\" role=\"dialog\">\n<button aria-label=\"Close model details\" class=\"model-modal-close\" data-model-modal-close=\"\" type=\"button\">\n        ×\n      </button>\n<div class=\"model-modal-media\" data-model-modal-viewport=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"model-modal-image\" src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-modal-content\">\n<span id=\"model-modal-category\">\n          CNC machining\n        </span>\n<h2 id=\"model-modal-title\">\n          Precision shaft parts\n        </h2>\n<p id=\"model-modal-description\">Multi-step shaft structure, including keyway, thread and chamfer features, suitable for CNC turning reference.</p>\n<dl class=\"model-modal-specs\">\n<div>\n<dt>File Format</dt>\n<dd id=\"model-modal-format\">STEP</dd>\n</div>\n<div>\n<dt>Recommended materials</dt>\n<dd id=\"model-modal-material\">Stainless steel</dd>\n</div>\n<div>\n<dt>downloaded capacity</dt>\n<dd id=\"model-modal-downloads\">1280</dd>\n</div>\n<div>\n<dt>Interaction</dt>\n<dd id=\"model-modal-interactions\">236 likes/42 comments</dd>\n</div>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"model-modal-actions\">\n<button class=\"btn btn-primary\" id=\"model-modal-fav\" type=\"button\">Favorite Models</button>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" download=\"\" href=\"/models/precision-shaft.step\" id=\"model-modal-download\">Download file</a>\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary model-modal-share\" data-model-share=\"\" id=\"model-modal-share\" type=\"button\">Share</button></div>\n<section class=\"model-modal-comments\">\n<h3>Comment Discussion</h3>\n<div id=\"model-modal-comment-list\">\n<p>\n<strong>CNC Process Engineer Chen:</strong>The keyway and chamfer processing of this model is relatively complete, which is suitable for shaft processing quotation reference.</p>\n<p>\n<strong>Structural Designer Leo:</strong>It is recommended to supplement the critical shaft diameter tolerance and heat treatment requirements in the actual project.</p>\n</div>\n<form class=\"model-comment-form\">\n<textarea aria-label=\"The content for the comment.\" placeholder=\"Write your comment or manufacturing suggestion...\"></textarea>\n<button class=\"btn btn-primary\" id=\"model-modal-comment-submit\" type=\"button\">Leave a Review</button>\n</form>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n"
}
